    <note>Meng(2) Zhonghou [8104] Yanbi's [3681] son, Song's [1364] father, Zhao(1) Zhezong's [9007] brother-in-law, Wang(2) Zhongni's [7373] son-in-law, Wang(2) Gui(1)'s [1845] grandson-in-law. Wang(2) Zhongni was buried in Suzhou and this branch of the Wang(2) originally from Chengdu, Huayang xian (and then Shuzhou), moved to Suzhou, as did the Meng(2), who were originally from Mingzhou in Hebei. Sun Di, WJ, 40.1a (wife, born Wang, who died in 1149 at age 54). CBD, 2, 1308-9.</note>
